description:
No Broker fee for an October move in !!

The owner is offering flexible lease terms ranging from 8 to 12 months, but please note that there will not be an option for renewal.

Discover your perfect urban oasis in the heart of South Boston! Unit 2A offers a blend of modern elegance and classic charm within a professionally managed building.

Upon entering, you'll be welcomed by abundant natural light streaming through large windows, showcasing stunning views of the Boston skyline. The open-concept layout enhances spaciousness, making it ideal for relaxation and entertaining. Characterized by exposed brick and contemporary finishes, the space is both inviting and stylish.

The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. Both bedrooms are spacious, while the spa-like bathroom provides a luxurious retreat.

Enjoy the newly renovated roof deck, an ideal setting for gatherings or simply taking in the views perfect for July 4th fireworks and St. Patrick's Day fun. For added convenience, there's a coin-operated washer and dryer in the building, along with a nearby Wash Dry Fold service.
Located in the vibrant South Boston neighborhood, you're just steps from popular restaurants like Lincoln, Loco, and Capo, and a CVS for all your essentials. Public bus routes are right outside your door, offering easy access to downtown, and you're close to Dorchester Heights Park and the beach.
Don't miss out on the chance to make Unit 2A your new home! Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience upscale South Boston living!

9-12 month lease
